parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay in remedying the Takata airbag recall can lead to serious or fatal injuries in the event of an accident, as the defective airbag inflators may rupture during deployment.
symptoms: as the issue is related to the recall remediation process.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power rear cargo door can cause serious injury or even death due to its large size and heavy weight, especially when it comes down without warning.
symptoms: The door falls or closes suddenly without warning
and does not retract back up when it hits something.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door handles can cause difficulty or impossibility in exiting the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The exterior door handle falls off
and self-extrication from the vehicle becomes unlikely.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rear lift door accessing unlocks on its own can cause accidents or injuries, especially when the door opens while driving.
symptoms: The rear lift door unlocks and opens on its own

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Black Chrome Paint on Window Frames Peeling
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The peeling of the black chrome paint on window frames can cause cosmetic issues and potentially lead to rust or corrosion.
symptoms: The black chrome paint on window frames peels away.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Heated Seat Module and Wiring Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the heated seat module and wiring can cause a fire hazard, potentially leading to injuries or damage to the vehicle.
symptoms: The heated seat function stops working
melted wires and burnt plugs are visible
no warning lights appear on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The erratic braking performance can cause accidents or loss of control, potentially leading to injuries or damage to the vehicle.
symptoms: The vehicle feels like it slips before the brakes kick in
especially when coming to a stop at lights and stop signs.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power outlet can cause inconvenience and potentially lead to electrical system failures.
